items.name: '-Register' and '-Login' functions - These tests covers the verification of features accessible directly from https://lennertamas.github.io/roxo/index.html url. Also verifies the url is correct.
'Logout' functions - These tests covers the verification of 'logout' function.
On Get in touch page sending a message must be possible.
'Registration' functions - These tests covers the verifications of registration related features and page behaviours.
'Input new data' functions - These tests covers the verification of inputting new data functions.
'Checking URL' functions - These tests covers the verification of the correct URL is loaded after navigation to the requested page.
'Repeated serial data entry from data source' functions - These tests covers the verification of the possibility to perform multiple inputs from data stored in a file.
When on landing page, the 'Home' button must navigate to the correct url.
'Delete profile' functions - These tests covers the verification of 'deleting user profile' functions.
'Data modification' functions - These tests covers the verification of 'data modification' functions.
